<HR>
<br />

<br />
<CENTER><span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: normal"><span style="color: red"><a name=petstats></a>Pet Statistics</span></span></CENTER>
<br />
<span style="font-size: 9px; line-height: normal">Special thanks to all mages that helped compile this list.</span>
<br />

<br />
<B>Disclaimer</b> This table is not complete, should you have any logged and verifiable information please <a href="mailto:xalmat@magecompendium.com">Email Me</a> and I will attempt to incorporate it until we have everything complete. Values with an x need to be reverified, while values with a * have been verified.
<br />

<br />
<B>Pet Basics - Common to all pets 1-49</b>
<br />
<B>All pre-50 pets are Warrior Class</b>
<br />
<ul><B>Air Pet</b> -<a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=967&amp;source=Live" target="_blank"> Air Elemental Attack</a>, <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=928&amp;source=Live" target="_blank">Air Elemental Invisibility</a>
<br />
<B>Earth Pet</b> - <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=969&amp;source=Live" target="_blank">Earth Elemental Attack</a>
<br />
<B>Fire Pet</b> - <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=966&amp;source=Live" target="_blank">Fire Elemental Attack</a>, <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=927&amp;source=Live" target="_blank">Fire Elemental Aura</a>
<br />
<B>Water Pet</b> - <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=968&amp;source=Live" target="_blank">Water Elemental Attack</a></ul>
<br />

<br />
<B>Pet Basics - Common to all pets 51-65</b>
<br />
<ul><B>Air Pet</b> - Warrior Class, <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=1020&amp;source=Live" target="_blank">Air Elemental Strike</a>, <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=928&amp;source=Live" target="_blank">Air Elemental Invisibility</a>
<br />
<B>Earth Pet</b> - Warrior Class, <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=1022&amp;source=Live" target="_blank">Earth Elemental Strike</a> (Rathe's Son casts <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=3193&amp;source=Live" target="_blank">Earth Elemental Strike 2</a>)
<br />
<B>Fire Pet</b> - Wizard Class, Casts various wizard spells
<br />
<B>Water Pet</b> - Rogue Class, <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/spell.html?id=1021&amp;source=Live" target="_blank">Water Elemental Strike</a></ul>
<br />

<br />
<i>Previously the pets had innate resistances,
<br />
<ul>Water : Nearly Immune to Posion
<br />
Earth : Nearly Immune Disease
<br />
Air : Nearly Immune Cold
<br />
Fire : Nearly Immune Fire</ul>
<br />

<br />
Since a recent patch however, pets supposedly use the greater of thier innate resistances and owners resists.  Verifying this actually works is somewhat of a enigma with the RNG of EQ and the shroud of mystery the developers like to keep us in. It should be noted that if the owner resists are high enough to resist a spell, then the pet will also resist that spell.</i>
<br />

<br />
Note:
<br />
<B>Bold</B> means this value has not been verified.
<br />

