				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Very nice work!
<br />

<br />
There is one more pet command you could add:
<br />

<br />
/pet as you were
<br />

<br />
Clears the command list of the pet (you can for example stack /pet attack orders if there are several mobs in camp, and if you want to change the order or something you can use this command to clear the command list). Note that this command does NOT clear the pet's aggro list like /pet back off does.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=423546" target="_blank" class="postlink">Izudin</a>, 65 Arch Convoker on Quellious</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
